{"tid":2484750,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"第N屆連登止蝕派vs strong hold派大賽現正開始，各位參賽選手同我入黎！！","createTime":"2021-04-11T19:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T11:36:18.000Z","uid":336484,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9b14394c6b10de52c7081387914c435d43b740bb","tid":2484750,"uid":336484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T19:16:10.000Z","msg":"咁多位參賽選手！！請大家下面留言講下對於止蝕派 and stronghold 派的意見！！我講先！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自古以來，止蝕派與strong hold派的紛爭無日無之，網絡平台上的對罵、冷嘲熱諷多不勝數，筆者無意吹捧或貶低某一派別，因為每一種派別均有其可取之處，應該用哪種玩法相當視乎個人因素，可以是心理質素、對股票的熱情，甚至是定力。以下我嘗試歸納各玩法的特質，方便新手了解：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>止蝕派</ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-傾向捕捉<span class=\"red\">短期行情</span>或動能（momentum），大多以技術分析作為進出場的依歸<br />\n-會為每個交易設立<span class=\"red\">止蝕</span>（一般為10%左右）<br />\n強調<span class=\"red\">紀律</span>，到達止蝕位置就必須賣出<br />\n-較為<span class=\"red\">靈活</span>，在一波大回調前期離場<br />\n<br />\n缺點：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n止蝕後<span class=\"red\">升返</span>是常有的事<br />\n比起strong hold派需要花更多<span class=\"red\">時間精力</span>在股票交易上<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>價值Strong hold 派</ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傾向進行<span class=\"red\">長期部署</span>（以年計）<br />\n了解公司的<span class=\"red\">基本面</span>，相信該公司未來的發展會向好，股價最終會反映<br />\n可以是月供自己相信的優質股或組合（例如月供契媽arkk）<br />\n基本上部署完就可以del app，較為節省時間及精力<br />\n<br />\ne.g.信契媽！買 tesla 放到2025<br />\n<br />\n缺點：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n股價在買入後有機會<span class=\"red\">短期內面臨大幅回調</span>，需要有心理準備承受短中期（可以是年計）虧損<br />\n<span class=\"red\">相當考驗選股能力</span>，是否買中真正優秀的公司股票需要數年後才能驗證<br />\n若考慮月供大盤或指數，需要考慮個人對於美市長遠發展的信心<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>半Strong hold派</ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-有點類似前兩者的混合，可以是以技術分析或價值分析為依歸入場<br />\n-相信美股只會升不會跌，總有機會返到家鄉<br />\n-跌幾多都不會走，直到返家鄉再另行部署<br />\n<br />\n簡單而言，止蝕派與價值strong hold派的分歧在於對於<span class=\"red\">交易時長的著眼</span>不同。止蝕派著重捕捉短期行情，價值派較為著重於股票的<span class=\"red\">長遠價值</span>。而半stronghold派著重於信仰（當然也可以是對某公司的信心）。<br />\n坦白說，我<span class=\"green\">們無法單以這三種模式完全概括股票的玩法分類</span>，因為不少人會將三種模式加以糅合、或因應市況，創造或採用屬於自己的玩法。但這三種模式的分類有助新手了解不同玩法的<span class=\"blue\">優點</span>、<span class=\"orange\">缺點</span>，從而根據自己的個人條件選擇合適的模式。<br />\n<br />\n未來我地會有更多文章分享，有興趣嘅喺下面留言。我地group喺一個<span class=\"red\">綜合性的股票資訊區</span>，會有每週trading idea 推薦，市況分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知更多？入埋我地嘅group！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/marketwizard2021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmarketwizard2021&d=WFG5iCHEkkmufTvr7zh8K51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=68e1302c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/marketwizard2021</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/marketwizard365/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmarketwizard365%2F&d=WFG5iCHEkkmufTvr7zh8K51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=6e091f8b\" target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/marketwizard365/</a>"},{"pid":"1704fe4d364a7d8920198d4a9ebdfe7c7d87d9e3","tid":2484750,"uid":372441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T19:18:22.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"blue\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>SS</strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"803f23c61566a199561bbd486dd73af170a3fdc4","tid":2484750,"uid":356010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T20:52:47.000Z","msg":"熊仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864e1a94bcdeeb57f1ceef926a01fe192cf9e050","tid":2484750,"uid":230594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T23:01:27.000Z","msg":"止蝕SH派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 